body:
Nice doc. To get [doxygen](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/developer-notes.md#coding-style-doxygen-compatible-comments) to pick this up, you'll have to do
```cpp
//! this
/// or this
/**
 * or this
 */
```

This is just a style/readability thing, but you can avoid indenting the next ~23 lines by changing this to 
```cpp
if (inv.type != MSG_TX && inv.type != MSG_WITNESS_TX) {
    continue;
}
```

